# Cognizant Digital Nurture 5.0 – Deep Skilling Program

## Overview

This repository contains my solutions, projects, and hands-on exercises completed as part of the **Cognizant Digital Nurture 5.0 (DN 5.0) Deep Skilling Program** under the **Python Full Stack Engineer Track**.

The program covers end-to-end software development concepts including:

* Python Programming
* Frontend Development
* Database Integration
* Backend Development
* ORM Integration
* MongoDB
* Query Optimization
* Migrations and Versioning
* Full Stack Application Development

